column5: Hey all, just got home so I can't give a full report, but I wanted to let you know that A-channel's Barrie news was there, and they covered the G2G and it will be on the 6 O'clock news.  I will give my full report later tonight when my Nephew's friends are gone, and he is bathing his 2yr old son.  Be back soon...if I'm still alive  Maureen
Gonna go catch it now, thanks Maureen.
I taped it...so I'll try to capture it on my computer tonite and post the story....nice little story they did...

Thanks fishfinder!!  I just finished eating and was about to capture it to upload on youtube.  Now I can relax for the evening...LOL.  Actually, Bly and I are getting ready to do some night fishing...hopefully a report later....
Darn, video runs for about 10 sec.'s, then hangs, AAARRRGGHH!!!!!
Hey that's great. More exposure will hopefully bring out more people.  I even showed my best side for the camera, the back side.
